{
  "chapter": 35,
  "chapter_summary": "本章写杨过化身神雕侠，与郭襄相见相知，因她坦率善良而赠三枚小龙女旧用金针，许她三件心愿。郭襄先求见杨过真容，继而牵挂其与小龙女重会，并由此种下深情。其后襄阳局势转急，霍都旧案、鲁有脚之死与丐帮帮主之争交织，杨过暗中相助，揭破阴谋。蒙古军逼城，郭靖、黄蓉等守御襄阳，郭襄又陷险境；杨过凭机智和武功周旋于敌营与战场之间，尼摩星等敌手相继受挫。本章以三枚金针贯穿儿女情义、江湖恩怨与家国危局，推动郭襄对杨过的敬慕及襄阳大战的紧张形势。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_shen_gui",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "最好是那霍都王子到来，大伙儿跟他斗斗，也好让史三哥出这口恶气⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_fu",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "让开！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_tou_gui",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她是冲着我而来，我去会会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是⋯⋯那是你姊姊么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有啊，我没为难之事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说罢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是在今年冬天。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "爸爸妈妈都好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "令姊又怎瞧得起我这般人了？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "十六年前，九月廿四，在襄阳大战金轮国师，龙儿抱着那孩儿⋯⋯",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但教力之所及，无不从命。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢你啦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guo",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没什么。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这自然由得你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这第三个心愿嘛⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姊姊，姊姊！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姊姊，我来啦，这几位都是好朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_tou_gui",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂，怎么⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要你知道姑奶奶的厉害！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_shao_jie",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还好！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的伤⋯⋯可真的不打紧吗？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么朋友？叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_fu",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "似乎是什么'西山一窟鬼'中的人物。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有这等事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘿嘿，霍都，霍都！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那霍都留下了什么言语没有？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_fu",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不信，那便走着瞧罢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我便识得一人，比姊夫好上十倍。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_fu",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是朱三弟么？是王剑民么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不！我说的那人，年纪比姊夫还小，模样儿长得比姊夫俊，武功可比姊夫强得多啦，简直是天差地远，比也不能比⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不见得希罕做丐帮帮主。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妈说那一天推选帮主？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_fu",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_fu",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是尼摩星？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "line_start": 561,
      "line_end": 561
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_mo_xing",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小娃儿不许多言的，快跟我走的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "line_start": 587,
      "line_end": 587
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姊姊，这人没了两条腿，别打他！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 595,
      "line_end": 595
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ni_mo_xing",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我叫你乖乖跟我走的⋯⋯",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "line_start": 613,
      "line_end": 613
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别怕！用暗器打他。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "line_start": 633,
      "line_end": 633
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "尼摩星，你捣什么鬼？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "line_start": 653,
      "line_end": 653
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_fu",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说外公来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 675,
      "line_end": 675
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是恩师到了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "line_start": 677,
      "line_end": 677
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 701,
      "line_end": 701
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_fu",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们拿去给妈妈瞧瞧，到底是谁，妈一猜便知。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 719,
      "line_end": 719
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "瞒什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 737,
      "line_end": 737
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她受了惊吓，自会心神不定。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 739,
      "line_end": 739
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孙三哥，羊祜，羊祜，这名字跟恩公不是音同⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 809,
      "line_end": 809
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "⋯⋯恩公从不差遣咱们干什么事，这一回务必⋯⋯大大的风光热闹⋯⋯挣个面子⋯⋯咱们的礼物⋯⋯",
      "tone": "低语",
      "line_start": 837,
      "line_end": 837
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我去拖二姊来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 911,
      "line_end": 911
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妈，真是奇怪！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 917,
      "line_end": 917
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现下再交朋友也还不迟啊。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "line_start": 945,
      "line_end": 945
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zi_liu",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好字，好字！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1047,
      "line_end": 1047
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些人你怎生识得的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "line_start": 1061,
      "line_end": 1061
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiang",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没什么古怪朋友啊，除非是姊夫。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "line_start": 1073,
      "line_end": 1073
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是百草仙送给你的生日礼啊。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1091,
      "line_end": 1091
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "竟有这等事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "line_start": 1099,
      "line_end": 1099
    }
  ],
